name: Diego Smith
summary: Diego Smith is a 29-year-old man from Boyle Heights, Los Angeles. He is a software developer who graduated from the University of California, Los Angeles. He values honesty, respect, and empathy and is keenly interested in coding, mountain biking, photography, and cooking. Diego identifies as agnostic, holds moderate political views, and intends to form a long-term relationship but is open to short-term ones as well. He is oriented to monogamy and is straight. As for his preferences, he expects his partner to be an active non-smoker, aged between 24 and 35, without children but open to having some. Despite being quite active, he enjoys spending free time with his pets: a dog and a cat.
